io.amcp.core

Class ControlEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.amcp.core.ControlEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class ControlEvent
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a control event used for managing agent lifecycle and system operations. Control events are system-level messages distinct from application events.
    Since:
    AMCP 1.0
